{"title":"ImportError_overview","date":"2019-12-28T09:27:25.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Dec 28, 2019","L":"12/28/2019","MM-DD":"12-28"},"link":"2019/12/28/ImportError-overview","tags":["Tensorflow"],"updated":"2019-12-30T13:21:21.165Z","content":"<p>在引入tensorflow相关资源包的时候，常常会因为各种原因报错，本文主要讲如何解决常见的此类错误。</p>\n\n\n<h1 id=\"ImportError-cannot-import-name-‘tf-utils’\">ImportError: cannot import name ‘tf_utils’<a href=\"2019/12/28/ImportError-overview#ImportError-cannot-import-name-‘tf-utils’\"></a></h1><p>Seems like it was a problem with keras 2.3.0, I installed keras 2.1.5 using pip and it works fine.</p>\n<p>pip install keras==2.1.5</p>\n<h1 id=\"No-module-named-‘colors’\">No module named ‘colors’<a href=\"2019/12/28/ImportError-overview#No-module-named-‘colors’\"></a></h1><p>pip install colors.py</p>\n","prev":{"title":"加密测试","link":"2019/12/30/加密测试"},"next":{"title":"Ubuntu软件源","link":"2019/12/28/Ubuntu软件源"},"plink":"https://thswind.github.io/2019/12/28/ImportError-overview/","toc":[{"title":"ImportError: cannot import name ‘tf_utils’","id":"ImportError-cannot-import-name-‘tf-utils’","index":"1"},{"title":"No module named ‘colors’","id":"No-module-named-‘colors’","index":"2"}],"reward":true}